SECTION 6 – POST CONSTRUCTION (FINAL INSPECTION AND HANDOVER)
SECTION 6 – POST CONSTRUCTION (FINAL INSPECTION AND HANDOVER)
Level foundation installed as per design. (Base layer only)
Drainage pipe wraped in filter sock to be installed along the base of the wall. (Base layer only)
Blocks Installed within specification tollerances & block pattern as per design drawings
The correct number & length of parawebs are to be installed as shown on the construction drawings.
Paraweb is to be placed flat or with a 1% fall toward the rear of the wall.
150mm of fill cover is required before construction equipment can travel over the area
Proof roll completed on each layer
